                </h4>
            </div>

            <div class="relative text-white bg-purple-900 bg-opacity-70 p-5 rounded border-2 shadow border-purple-600 w-full sm:w-2/3 h-64 mx-auto my-8">
                <p class="text-center text-xl font-semibold">How to Win:</p>
                <ol class="text-left list-decimal p-4 flex flex-col gap-2" type="1">
                    <li>Sign up with your email</li>
                    <li>Collect your daily free spins</li>
                    <li>Spin the reels on our exciting slot machines</li>
                    <li>Match the winning symbols</li>
                    <li>Celebrate your massive $1,000,000 win!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
